    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>At your command, light shoots through a small glass prism, shooting a rainbow light at your target. The bolt has a different effect based on the dominant color reflected.</em></p><p><strong>Ranged Spell Attack</strong></p><p>When you cast this spell, you roll [[/r 1d8]] to determine the damage type.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d20]] damage (or [[/damage 1d20 + 5 radiant]]{1d20 + 5} if you rolled an 8 for radiant damage).*</p></li></ul><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>D8 Result</strong></p></td><td data-colwidth=\"349\"><p><strong>Damage Type</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"349\"><p>&amp;reference[Fire] (Red)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"349\"><p>&amp;reference[Thunder] (Orange)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"349\"><p>&amp;reference[Lightning] (Yellow)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>4</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"349\"><p>&amp;reference[Acid] (Green)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"349\"><p>&amp;reference[Cold] (Blue)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"349\"><p>&amp;reference[Force] (Indigo)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>7</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"349\"><p>&amp;reference[Necrotic] (Purple)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>8</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"349\"><p>&amp;reference[Radiant] (White or Rainbow), and add +5 to the spell's damage.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d20]] for each spell level above 1st.</p>",
